# fold.word — what a fold IS: one chain read into the present.
# Axiom: it bottoms out in the host (the projection/reducer, loadOrFold + foldEngine). The
# place is folded from facts, never stored. Descends from word.word, base.word, chain.word;
# every word grounded (fold, chain, fact, order, head). `present` is the floor (time).

A fold is a chain read into the present, its facts taken in order from first to head, each changing what is.
A fold is the present of one chain.
A fold is read into a cache, never the truth. The facts are the truth. The fold is only their reading, kept so the next read takes up where the last left off, not from the first.
